      "content": "i was looking at some old photos today and i didnt even recognize the person in them. it feels like that version of me actually died a long time ago. now i'm just... going through the motions. like i'm just a ghost or a walking corpse haunting my own life. it's so exhausting to pretend to be alive when there's nothing left inside.",
